pageContext.claim: “Highest Stock Market In History, By Far!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump often claims that the stock market has notched record highs. The stock market is doing well, but his scorekeeping is fishy. According to the Balance, a personal finance website, the Dow Jones had broken 44 records from the time Trump took office through Jan. 9, 2020. The most recent high was Feb. 12 not Feb. 19.
